com.citytechinc.cq.component.annotations.widgets

Annotation Type RichTextEditor


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface RichTextEditor
    Represents a Widget of type CQ.form.RichText in Classic UI This widget is not supported in Touch UI and will render as a textarea
